A final year student of Kogi State University, Abdullahi Muhammed Awwal, has been murdered by unknown gunmen. CAMPUSLIFE gathered that the deceased, popularly known as ‘Comrade Lincoln’, was killed near NTA office, Anyigba, Kogi. There have been reactions following his death. While some said he was killed by hoodlums, others claimed he was shot by cultists. The deceased has been laid to rest in his hometown, according to Islamic rites.